    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i've read online that medical grade honey is actually really good for wounds because it's antibacterial and helps with healing. is there a specific type or amount i should use if i just want to try that first? it's not super wide, just deep. i'm just trying to avoid the hospital bill if i can help it.",
